## Color Palette

### Backgrounds (dark mode)
```css
--background:          18 18 20;   /* #121214 - primary surface */
--background-elevated: 28 28 30;   /* #1C1C1E - cards, panels */
--background-tertiary: 44 44 46;   /* #2C2C2E - nested elements */
