### Text Hierarchy
```css
--foreground:           255 255 255;    /* Primary text - white */
--foreground-secondary: 160 160 165;    /* #A0A0A5 - secondary text */
--foreground-tertiary:  110 110 115;    /* #6E6E73 - tertiary/disabled */
