## Typography

### Font Stack
```css
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, 
             "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
```

### Type Scale
| Use Case          | Size      | Weight     | Color                  |
|-------------------|-----------|------------|------------------------|
| Page title        | 20-24px   | semibold   | white                  |
| Section heading   | 14-16px   | semibold   | white                  |
| Body text         | 14px      | normal     | white/90               |
| Secondary text    | 12-13px   | normal     | white/50-60            |
| Labels            | 10px      | medium     | white/40, uppercase    |
| Metric values     | 24-32px   | light      | white, tabular-nums    |
| Code/monospace    | 12px      | normal     | font-mono              |

### Label Convention
Small labels (like "DETECTIONS", "LATENCY") use:
```css
text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40
```

