## Do's and Don'ts

### Do
- Use white/[opacity] for text (e.g., `text-white/80`)
- Use bg-white/[0.02-0.08] for subtle backgrounds
- Use indigo-400/500 as the sole accent color
- Keep borders very subtle (0.06-0.08 opacity)
- Use `tabular-nums` for numeric displays
- Use uppercase tracking-wider for small labels

### Don't
- Don't use pure black (#000000) backgrounds
- Don't use drop shadows for elevation
- Don't use multiple accent colors
- Don't use heavy borders (>0.1 opacity)
- Don't use bounce animations
- Don't use font sizes below 9px

